data.description: Don't miss your chance at this renovated 3-bed, 1-bath home in Titusville. This home offers a recently renovated bathroom and newer kitchen. Enjoy peace of mind with a brand-new metal roof, HVAC system, and ductwork all installed in 2023! Exterior was freshly painted in 2023! Indoor laundry/ utility room. Centrally located close to shopping, restaurants, Playalinda Beach, and space center launches. The spacious corner lot boasts a beautiful oak hammock with room to relax and expand.
